{"tid":1591151,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"覺得有d疲累就入嚟睇下","createTime":"2019-09-24T04:45:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-24T04:48:21.000Z","uid":307637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"e3880756e257fd2278f441975a2edf9bed2e9b5b","tid":1591151,"uid":307637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T04:45:59.000Z","msg":"本人是一個十分喜愛鋼之鍊金術師的人，我認為現在香港的狀況，十分像鋼鍊之中的情況，明知人造人(共產黨)好強，布拉多萊(林鄭)好撚勁，軍隊(popo)又大多衹服從中央，中央叫佢地做乜都照做，一d思考冇，中央班高官(香港高官)當然知人造人(共產黨)既陰謀，但為咗自己利益，而選擇犧牲人民，而俾人造人一夜亡國既克賽爾克賽斯就好似新疆。<br />\n<br />\n坩結局我地？<br />\n錯，我地很大機會輸，因為我地冇軍隊，亦冇賀恩漢，我地可以依靠衹有自己對手，我地既辛苦一定比阿美尼斯特尼斯人多，背負既嘢一定比佢地多，但我地吾可以輸，我地輸，呢度就玩完，香港警察正式會成為城管，可以隨時入屋吊你老婆再打七你，而你飲食都吾會再有保障，貪污情況會返去以前1972年坩。<br />\n<br />\n我都覺好累，好想停，但我知吾可以，所以我會聽呢兩首歌鼓勵自己，死都要頂落去，好快，好快我地會贏，我地會拿返屬於我地嘅香港。<br />\n香港人加油!<br />\n<br />\n最後送俾你地兩首歌:<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=OBQ7YAGRy9Y&amp;list=PLwI8okPbv5YbvEqkmH9PvYMyNOm4JpSZB&amp;index=13&amp;t=14s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DOBQ7YAGRy9Y%26list%3DPLwI8okPbv5YbvEqkmH9PvYMyNOm4JpSZB%26index%3D13%26t%3D14s&d=CxVPqDM3fecqSGKEY7rAqIeNTHq1rgEicHo%2BkVhR8rs%3D&h=e969afd5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=OBQ7YAGRy9Y&amp;list=PLwI8okPbv5YbvEqkmH9PvYMyNOm4JpSZB&amp;index=13&amp;t=14s</a><br />\n同埋我地勝後嘅景象:<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=oM03ETAc-f0&amp;list=PLwI8okPbv5YbvEqkmH9PvYMyNOm4JpSZB&amp;index=12&amp;t=0s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DoM03ETAc-f0%26list%3DPLwI8okPbv5YbvEqkmH9PvYMyNOm4JpSZB%26index%3D12%26t%3D0s&d=CxVPqDM3fecqSGKEY7rAqIeNTHq1rgEicHo%2BkVhR8rs%3D&h=47c5587c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=oM03ETAc-f0&amp;list=PLwI8okPbv5YbvEqkmH9PvYMyNOm4JpSZB&amp;index=12&amp;t=0s</a><br />\n(記得留意歌詞同希望各位幫手推一推)"},{"pid":"1690054941dfa27ac2662dd3f7a386e1fc70989c","tid":1591151,"uid":307637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24